Georges Saillard https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georges_Saillard 0 Georges Augustin Eugène Saillard (July 5, 1877 - September 11, 1967) was a French film actor. He starred in some 52 films between 1909 and 1950. He died in Versailles on September 11, 1967 Georges_Augustin_Eugène_Saillard ( July_5_,_1877 - September_11_,_1967 ) was a_French_film_actor .
